Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll turn the tides with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire Zombie Army’s attack is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, you zombie freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Screw Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we’re leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they’ll be trapped in that cave for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tag Duel in the Labyrinth!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t moving an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can only look for another exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How are we supposed to search for one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus’ castle is most likely this way, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always protected me, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you were around, I was always happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big… Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you, Big Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Bakura, is it really ok to go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve been walking for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus the pathway’s getting smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The walls have changed in landscape, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all disorganized before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then they became like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're man-made...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is kinda… like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, which way now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit’s this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the exit really this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guardians of the caverns…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Labyrinth Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Labyrinth Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A comedy duo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Star Chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they player killers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my. It sure is rare for the rats to wander into our maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but they are far from lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost ones, can you determine the correct path?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The correct path!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel us for the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a duel ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those doors is the correct way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, we’ll tell you which one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose or run, you’ll wander the depths of the cave for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we can’t leave if we can’t win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this will be a two on two match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two duelists, please step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two on two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tag match?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, it could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we have no choice but accept the match, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as they want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to out Labyrinth Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Where do you see a labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll see soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, place your star chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll bet two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll bet on four!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet six!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win this, we’ll both have ten star chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we can head for Pegasus’ castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won’t be happening. After all, we’re the Labyrinth Player Killers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don’t know what they’re getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and beat them, so we can get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my turn to start off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Labyrinth Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Labyrinth Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The walls of a maze…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Labyrinth Wall can only be summoned on this type of field.*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our Labyrinth Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain the new rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each player has 2000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if any player loses all of their life, then his tag team loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! So if I lose, then Yugi loses too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are also permitted to use your teammate's cards on your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, onto the Labyrinth Field rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, each Duel Monster will move like a chess piece on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that card is summoned, it can move in accordance to its star level.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters battle when they meet up on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also win by getting to the end and deciding which one of the doors is the correct exit at the end of the Labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which door you choose is for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll say if you picked the correct door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, that’s dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re betting our lives on this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least give us a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from here on out…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us will be telling the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one will tell nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must you have such a scary face over this mere turn of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, you’ll have to figure out which one will tell nothing but the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And which one will tell nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn’t a lie just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Nothing but the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, my Mei door is the true exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, my Kyuu door is the true exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve heard this quiz before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I’m right…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A traveler was lost at the crossroads between the village of truth, and the village of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The traveler wanted to ask a villager at the crossroads, but couldn’t tell which village he was from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The traveler wanted to get the village of truth, and was allowed to ask the man one question.*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he asked was…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Take me to your village!”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, if he was telling the truth, he would take you to the village of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he was lying, he would take you to the village of truth, because it isn’t his village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, I have a question for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will allow one question from each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:12:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have you tell us which one of yours is the real exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of you is protecting the true exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, they’ll both point at the true exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real exit is the Kyuu exit, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’ll be easy to get out of here!*
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kyuu exit…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the true exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of them really was on our side, then what you said would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think its okay to just believe them so blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the village of truth quiz you’re referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the differences between that and the situation at hand are lethal for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, in the original,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one person at the crossroads. In our case, there are two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can’t from their words if they’re from either the village of truth, or from the village of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there’s something else that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To know that one was lying, they would have to both be from the village of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there’s also the possibility that they’re both from the village of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, then there’s no way of knowing which way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s continue this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be swindled by their words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll eventually find out which one is the real door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t figure it out now, no matter how much we think on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The duel continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we have to beat them before we can leave this dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon the card Ruiz in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not attack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue with your monster’s movement in accordance to its star level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then. He’s 4 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luis, move forward 4 spaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you the horrifying strength of the labyrinth field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Shadow Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I fuse him to the Labyrinth Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Shadow, Labyrinth Wind Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luis is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that’s cheating, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Wall Shadow is the wall itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even more so, there are no spaces on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Shadow…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s now impossible to walk within the walls without the possibility of being destroyed in one fatal slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a labyrinth, so it’s natural for it to have a guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It is impossible to leave this labyrinth alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it’s my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Axe Raider in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I set one more card face down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t attack what I can’t see. Therefore, I won’t move this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way I'm safe from your wall-jumping freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can’t attack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right, Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t get close, the Wall Shadow can’t attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what I’m thinking, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Jounouchi doesn’t screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright. Yugi will follow up if that’s the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In tag matches, they usually aim for the weaker prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I set a card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the trap, Land-mine Spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more cards they bring in, the more they will lose to the monster form of Jirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Labyrinth Tank, and move him ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you stand no chance of leaving this maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Elf Swordsman in attack mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move ahead 4 spaces into the Labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Elf Swordsman doesn’t have the attack points to beat the Wall Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the same thing will…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Shadow, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your target is the Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an ignorant fool. Now the Elf Swordsman is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chained Equipped Boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The Wall Shadow is trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I set before was the Chained Boomerang, intended to power up my monsters, and trap my opponent’s!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it on Yugi’s Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Elf Swordsman has 500 more attack onto his original 1400!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bury the Wall Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Shadow is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great combination has just been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, you really have become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The duel has all but started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct, let the game continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll show you that we’re the greatest tag team out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll win with our combined strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is looking to be very interesting indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he still hasn’t been found, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re looking with everything we have, so please just wait a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy will definitely come out at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}certain{\i0} of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t lose to something this weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. My brother will definitely come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother would always come when I really needed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not give they key to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, I’ll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(141,137)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Jounouchi kill beating all of the Labyrinth monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're winning play after play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't look like they're gonna win that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the three boxes became one huge monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s the ace of the Labyrinth Brothers, The Gate Guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:50.43,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Demon God Fusion! The Gate Guardian
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.06,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
