Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
